{"tid":495663,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小孩都念大學了　她卻和8年級男同事上旅館","createTime":"2017-12-11T01:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T10:16:27.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec5f9e9d89d8ff065d33ad8b3eada06fb9f070c","tid":495663,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:53:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>小孩都念大學了　她卻和8年級男同事上旅館</strong><br />\n<br />\n北市一名保養得宜的已婚蘇姓熟女，和丈夫育有一對兒女，某日已就讀大學的女兒卻在媽媽手機內發現驚人秘密，媽媽竟和一名年輕男子用LINE曖昧對談，甚至相約到旅館 ，女兒向爸爸舉報，蘇夫查出和妻子進出旅館的小王，竟年僅25歲、是妻子的余姓男同事，蘇夫怒告通姦，但兩人辯稱只是女方肚子痛去上廁所。台北地檢署認為罪嫌不足，不起訴兩人。<br />\n<br />\n蘇夫提告指控，妻子那段時間時常晚歸，他已覺得不太尋常，不料女兒告訴他媽媽和別的男人約去旅館，讓他更確信妻子出軌，果然在妻子的LINE中看到兩人互訴曖昧之情，包括「反正你要定我了」、「你娶我」等語，且對話中顯示，兩人今年2月間和7月間還兩度相約去旅館。<br />\n<br />\n最讓蘇夫無法忍受的是，兩人的孩子都已就讀大學、高中，妻子曖昧的對象竟然是個8年級的男同事，雖然妻子堅稱兩人只是同事沒出軌，但蘇夫仍決定提告。<br />\n<br />\n開庭時，蘇女和余男雖然承認有去旅館，但稱當下只是女方肚子痛又有潔癖，所以才會去旅館解決，沒有發生其他事情。<br />\n<br />\n檢方認為，即便兩人有去旅館，但沒有證據能證明兩人有發生性關係，因此以罪嫌不足不起訴兩人。（吳珮如／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.go2yd.com/image.php?url=0GtCGfOMPX\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.go2yd.com%2Fimage.php%3Furl%3D0GtCGfOMPX&h=a5d13bdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60471ccda0122e3091511577b206d4855bcabb86","tid":495663,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625f43ca46ec62511ae2f99b575e02956deb27b9","tid":495663,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"個官真英明"},{"pid":"65c42812bd73212f818ea6f86a9746bb64f2e8f4","tid":495663,"uid":101390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"又一分"},{"pid":"cb62267c4971c6569a904ec138f8ae9b0c951b46","tid":495663,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"冇示意圖？"},{"pid":"0b0261aff77aae4a3b1395fe020d7869c4353ff8","tid":495663,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"個官弱智架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7470b060555c47c73e488107e0ee7c183550d1d4","tid":495663,"uid":2656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"台灣真係好有趣"},{"pid":"dc6af34dd0db8fcc0e8e53124e17cd373e024875","tid":495663,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:09:03.000Z","msg":"d flirt msg唔可以做證據?"},{"pid":"42dd357ff0df585868ad77e5fcfbbf36a0d49495","tid":495663,"uid":156376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"8年級仲以為係小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cb397fd929514e75bf147652597f2b6d8fd81c","tid":495663,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d flirt msg唔可以做證據?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> flirt下人就等如屌左人個西？咁我年中屌唔少女人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519ad6fc6af6396bcbe2dcba79d75d44eb31e90f","tid":495663,"uid":14274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:16:27.000Z","msg":"2-7月約兩次咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}